To install node packages:

  $ npm install

To start the database: 

  $ docker-compose up -d

To run the dev server:

  $ npm run dev

To run the 'production' server:

  $ npm start

To view the testing page:

  http://localhost:3010/api/v0/api-docs

To run tests and examine code coverage:

  $ npm test

To run the linter:

  $ npm run lint

To stop the database: 

  $ docker-compose down
